Class ParameterNaiveActionIdMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.stochasticgames.agents.naiveq.history.ParameterNaiveActionIdMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ActionIdMap

    public class ParameterNaiveActionIdMap
extends java.lang.Object
implements ActionIdMap
    An action to int map that takes the list of possible action names in a domain and assigns and int value to them. This method will not manage object identifier independence.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
